      • setEventLoopGroup

        public Config setEventLoopGroup(io.netty.channel.EventLoopGroup eventLoopGroup)
        Use external EventLoopGroup. EventLoopGroup processes all Netty connection tied with Redis servers. Each EventLoopGroup creates own threads and each Redisson client creates own EventLoopGroup by default. So if there are multiple Redisson instances in same JVM it would be useful to share one EventLoopGroup among them.

        Only EpollEventLoopGroup or NioEventLoopGroup can be used.

        Parameters:
        eventLoopGroup -
        Returns:
